'''Most High Proctor''' was the title given to rulers of [[Thebeon 8]]. The Most High Proctor of Thebeon 8 during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] attended the [[Thirteenth Imperial Diplomatic Conclave]] hosted by [[Thalassa Tarkin|Lady Tarkin]] on [[Phelarion/Legends|Phelarion]].

